{"comments":"Straylight typographical conventions\n\nThis module encodes the precise formatting rules for straylight code.\nAll lines are exactly 80 characters. Titles are right-aligned to column 80.\n\n## Line Types\n\n- **Heavy (`━`)**: File-level framing, module boundaries\n- **Double (`═`)**: Major sections within a file  \n- **Light (`─`)**: Subsections, nested structure\n\n## Usage\n\n```purescript\nimport Hydrogen.Convention as C\n\n-- Generate headers\nC.heavyHeader \"// hydrogen // color\"\n-- \"-- ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\"\n-- \"--                                                          // hydrogen // color\"\n-- \"-- ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\"\n\n-- Validate a title line\nC.validateTitle \"--                                                          // hydrogen // color\"\n-- Right unit (valid)\n\nC.validateTitle \"--                                                         // hydrogen // color\"\n-- Left \"Line is 79 characters, expected 80\"\n```\n","declarations":[{"children":[],"comments":"Canonical line width for all straylight code\n\nAll lines are exactly 80 characters. No exceptions.\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Int"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[76,17],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Convention.purs","start":[76,1]},"title":"lineWidth"},{"children":[],"comments":"Comment prefix for PureScript/Haskell: \"-- \"\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"String"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[80,24],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Convention.purs","start":[80,1]},"title":"commentPrefix"},{"children":[],"comments":"Length of comment prefix: 3\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Int"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[84,24],"name":"../../